## 2. Advanced Capabilities & Constructors

Forui offers specialized constructors for complex use cases. Use these patterns instead of building from scratch.

### A. Forms & Selection

| Feature | Implementation Pattern | Use Case |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Async Search** | `FSelect.search(filter: (q) async => ...)` | Network-based dropdowns (e.g., API search). |
| **Rich Items** | `FSelect.rich(children: [FSelectSection(...)])` | Dropdowns with headers/dividers. |
| **Lazy Lists** | `FSelectMenuTile.builder(count: ..., builder: ...)` | Long lists in mobile menus. |
| **Form Integration**| `FTextFormField`, `FSelect`, `FDateField` | Validated inputs inside `Form` widget. |
| **Validation** | `autovalidateMode: AutovalidateMode.onUserInteraction` | Real-time feedback. |

### B. Navigation & Structure

| Feature | Implementation Pattern | Use Case |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Nested Header** | `FHeader.nested(prefixes: [FHeaderAction.back(...)])` | Sub-pages, Details views. |
| **Lazy Group** | `FTileGroup.builder(...)` | Long settings lists or results. |
| **Merged Groups** | `FTileGroup.merge(children: [...])` | Combining multiple data sources visually. |
| **Scaffold Tabs** | `FScaffold(footer: FBottomNavigationBar(...))` | Main app navigation structure. |

### C. Overlays (Dialogs, Sheets, Toasts)

| Feature | Implementation Pattern | Use Case |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Adaptive Dialog** | `FDialog.adaptive(...)` | Auto-adjusts layout for screen size. |
| **Raw Toast** | `showRawFToast(builder: (context, entry) => ...)` | Totally custom notification UI. |
| **Sticky Toast** | `showFToast(duration: null)` | Non-dismissible alerts (e.g., upload progress). |
| **Draggable Sheet**| `showFSheet(builder: (_) => DraggableScrollableSheet(...))` | Resizable bottom sheets. |

