## 3. Touch-First Mobile Patterns

For mobile layouts (PharmaScan target), strictly prefer these "Touch-First" widgets over desktop equivalents.

| Desktop / Form Pattern | **Mobile / Touch Pattern** | Why? |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `FRadio` | **`FSelectTileGroup`** | Larger touch target, full width. |
| `FCheckbox` | **`FSwitch`** | Swipe gesture support, standard mobile UX. |
| `FSelect` (Dropdown) | **`FSelectMenuTile`** | Opens a bottom sheet/menu, easier to reach. |
| `FCard` (List Item) | **`FTile`** | Built-in interactions, states, and standard height. |
| `Calendar` | **`FDateField.input`** | Keyboard entry is often faster than tapping dates. |

